259
00:18:10,013 --> 00:18:11,513
With my baton up your ass!

260
00:18:11,598 --> 00:18:13,265
FAT ASS: Let me out of here!

261
00:18:13,349 --> 00:18:16,727
What is your malfunction,
you fat barrel of monkey spunk?

262
00:18:16,811 --> 00:18:17,978
FAT ASS: Please...

263
00:18:18,062 --> 00:18:20,105
