264
00:18:20,189 --> 00:18:21,565
Not me!

265
00:18:21,649 --> 00:18:24,109
I ain't gonna count to three, or even one.

266
00:18:24,193 --> 00:18:26,486
Shut the fuck up, or I'll sing you a lullaby!

267
00:18:26,571 --> 00:18:28,405
(Whispers) Shut up, man. Shut up.

268
00:18:28,489 --> 00:18:29,781
There's been a mistake!

269
00:18:29,866 --> 00:18:33,035
You don't understand.
I'm not supposed to be here!

270
00:18:33,119 --> 00:18:34,202
Open that cell.

271
00:18:34,287 --> 00:18:38,457
MAN: Me neither.
You people run this place like a fucking prison!

272
00:18:45,924 --> 00:18:47,966
HADLEY: Son of a bitch.

273
00:18:48,051 --> 00:18:49,927
(Thuds)

274
00:18:50,011 --> 00:18:52,054
(Whimpering)

275
00:18:52,138 --> 00:18:54,222
PRISONER: Take it easy.

276
00:18:59,562 --> 00:19:01,229
(Yelps)

277
00:19:16,996 --> 00:19:20,374
If I hear so much as a mouse fart in here
the rest of the night,

278
00:19:20,458 --> 00:19:24,127
I swear by God and sonny Jesus,
you will all visit the infirmary.

279
00:19:24,212 --> 00:19:26,296
Every last motherfucker in here.

280
00:19:30,218 --> 00:19:33,887
Call the trustees.
Take that tub of shit down to the infirmary.

281
00:19:48,194 --> 00:19:52,906
RED: His first night in the joint,
Andy Dufresne cost me two packs of cigarettes.

282
00:19:52,991 --> 00:19:55,867
He never made a sound.

283
00:19:58,746 --> 00:20:00,831
