284
00:20:11,384 --> 00:20:14,636
GUARD: Tier 3 North. Clear.

285
00:20:14,721 --> 00:20:16,888
Tier 2 South. Clear.

286
00:20:16,973 --> 00:20:18,849
Tier 3 South. Clear.

287
00:20:18,933 --> 00:20:20,892
Tier 1 North...

288
00:20:20,977 --> 00:20:23,770
- Tier 1 South. Clear.
- Tier 4 South. Clear.

289
00:20:23,855 --> 00:20:25,939
Prepare to roll out.

290
00:20:29,318 --> 00:20:31,403
GUARD: Roll out!

