00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:27,084
Are... Are you going to eat that?

292
00:21:27,168 --> 00:21:30,087
I hadn't... I hadn't planned on it.

293
00:21:31,339 --> 00:21:32,380
Do you mind?

294
00:21:39,722 --> 00:21:42,349
Ah...that's nice and ripe.

295
00:21:47,105 --> 00:21:49,189
