00:21:53,945 --> 00:21:56,404
Jake says thank you.

297
00:21:56,489 --> 00:21:58,907
Fell out of his nest over by the plate shop.

298
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:05,705
I'm going to look after him
until he's big enough to fly.

299
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,582
Oh, no, no. Here he comes.

300
00:22:10,711 --> 00:22:14,631
Morning, fellas. Fine morning, ain't it?

301
00:22:14,715 --> 00:22:17,134
You know why it's a fine morning, don't you?

302
00:22:17,218 --> 00:22:19,636
Come on. Set 'em down.
