304
00:22:22,598 --> 00:22:24,683
Yeah, look at that!

305
00:22:24,767 --> 00:22:27,644
- Look at that. Oh, Lord!
- I can't stand this guy.

306
00:22:27,728 --> 00:22:28,770
(Inhales)

307
00:22:28,855 --> 00:22:31,523
Yes. Richmond, Virginia.

308
00:22:31,607 --> 00:22:33,692
- Smell my ass!
- After he smells mine.

309
00:22:33,776 --> 00:22:39,114
Gee, Red, it was a terrible shame
about your horse coming in last, an' all.

310
00:22:39,198 --> 00:22:42,409
But I sure do love that winning horse of mine,
though.

311
00:22:42,493 --> 00:22:45,203
I owe that boy a great big, sloppy kiss
when I see him.

312
00:22:45,288 --> 00:22:48,290
Why don't you give him some of your cigarettes,
instead?

313
00:22:48,374 --> 00:22:50,167
Lucky fuck.

314
00:22:50,251 --> 00:22:51,960
Hey, Tyrell.

315
00:22:52,044 --> 00:22:55,005
You pull infirmary duty this week?

316
00:22:55,089 --> 00:22:56,798
How's that horse of mine doing?

317
00:22:56,883 --> 00:22:58,341
