Duettino from The Marriage Of Figaro

980
01:07:51,825 --> 01:07:54,410
â™ª Sull'aria...

981
01:07:58,039 --> 01:07:59,039
Andy,

982
01:07:59,124 --> 01:08:00,457
do you hear that?

983
01:08:00,542 --> 01:08:04,253
â™ª ..zeffiretto

984
01:08:12,721 --> 01:08:14,555
(Locks door)

985
01:08:16,474 --> 01:08:24,315
â™ª Questa sera spirera

986
01:08:33,033 --> 01:08:34,366
(Feedback hisses)

987
01:08:36,578 --> 01:08:39,496
(Music over loudspeakers)

988
01:08:43,501 --> 01:08:45,586
(Aria continues)

